attachments.title: What is New in Android: Hack@home Event *Official Site*  - Google+
attachments.text: Join us for a two-hour live-streamed developer event, wherever you are; home, office, school. You will be able to test the new Android M Developer Preview announced at Google I/O and ask the Googlers who built it.
